name: Rokhi
description: Rokhi is a project that helps creative industry as a whole. Among the projects that will be implemented are the production of creative service applications named RONIC, an online store (Rokhi Store) that sells physical creative works, and Rokhi NFT gallery. This will help creative activists to generate income virtually. Rokhi token can be used to purchase creative products listed on the website or by visiting our partners online store to get a special discounts on their products.
